{"title":"故乡","authors":["沙鸥"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":4,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙鸥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"途中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是这条黄泥巴路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路边还是这根桂花树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么亲热的地方呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一块田我都记得清楚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社办公室就在那座瓦房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见了那扇笑着的窗户。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰见一个熟人该多好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想说的话能装几间屋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李大妈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在土湾的堰塘边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇见了李大妈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她认出是我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把拉到了她的家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她把甚么都指给我看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把新过门的儿媳妇夸了又夸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起那个落雪的年三十……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她说不是毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骨头早烂啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笔直的土红色的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸向一片杏黄色的草屋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路边一排长长的瓜架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的丝瓜花千万朵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一条多好看的花边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把青青的山林拦住。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜悦藏在一位共青团员心中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她早算好了为社增加多少数目。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她走着均匀的脚步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她围着磨盘流着汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的脸是红红的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的眼珠是亮亮的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她刚刚离开学校，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的“青年近卫军”在桌子上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她喜爱那四十条奶牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她喜爱等着吃奶的婴儿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新居"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白的墙，朱红的屋檐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜鹊在黑瓦上唱歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个红领巾背上书包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在门口笑嘻嘻地喊我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹娘都上地去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婆婆在家里也忙着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我轻脚轻手走进后院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见一群小猪摇着尾巴围着婆婆。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}